      <section id="details">
        <h2 class="gem-c-heading gem-c-heading--font-size-27 gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  ">Details</h2>


        
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
    
          <div class="govspeak">
<p>This guide is for approved driving instructors (<abbr title="approved driving instructors">ADIs</abbr>), motorcycle trainers, and lorry and bus (vocational) trainers. It explains:</p>

<ul>
  <li>how you should work safely during coronavirus</li>
  <li>what support is available for businesses</li>
</ul>

</div>

</div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="app-c-published-dates app-c-published-dates--history" id="history" data-module="toggle" lang="en">
    Published 10 July 2020
    <br></br>Last updated 3 November 2020
      <a href="#full-history" class="app-c-published-dates__toggle govuk-link" data-controls="full-history" data-expanded="false" data-toggled-text="- hide all updates">+ show all updates</a>
      <div class="app-c-published-dates__change-history js-hidden" id="full-history">
        <ol>
            <li class="app-c-published-dates__change-item">
              <time class="app-c-published-dates__change-date timestamp" datetime="2020-11-03T12:11:39.000+00:00">3 November 2020</time>
              <p class="app-c-published-dates__change-note">Added information about the suspension of theory tests in England from 5 November 2020. They'll start again on 2 December 2020.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="app-c-published-dates__change-item">
              <time class="app-c-published-dates__change-date timestamp" datetime="2020-11-02T16:43:38.000+00:00">2 November 2020</time>
              <p class="app-c-published-dates__change-note">Added information about the suspension of driving lessons and driving tests in England from 5 November to 2 December 2020.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="app-c-published-dates__change-item">
              <time class="app-c-published-dates__change-date timestamp" datetime="2020-10-30T17:39:49.000+00:00">30 October 2020</time>
              <p class="app-c-published-dates__change-note">Added information about the law changing in Scotland from 2 November 2020 so that driving instructors and their pupils must wear face coverings during driving lessons and practice sessions, unless they have a good reason not to.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="app-c-published-dates__change-item">
              <time class="app-c-published-dates__change-date timestamp" datetime="2020-10-22T17:28:42.000+01:00">22 October 2020</time>
              <p class="app-c-published-dates__change-note">Updated to explain that driver and rider training and tests will be suspended in Wales because of the coronavirus firebreak.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="app-c-published-dates__change-item">
              <time class="app-c-published-dates__change-date timestamp" datetime="2020-09-14T00:15:06.000+01:00">14 September 2020</time>
              <p class="app-c-published-dates__change-note">Removed content about service restart dates as services now restarted.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="app-c-published-dates__change-item">
              <time class="app-c-published-dates__change-date timestamp" datetime="2020-08-20T17:41:41.000+01:00">20 August 2020</time>
              <p class="app-c-published-dates__change-note">Updated to explain that the driving test booking service will be available for new bookings from 8am on 21 August 2020. Added the dates that driving lessons and tests will restart in Scotland.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="app-c-published-dates__change-item">
              <time class="app-c-published-dates__change-date timestamp" datetime="2020-08-14T10:00:02.000+01:00">14 August 2020</time>
              <p class="app-c-published-dates__change-note">Updated the section on timescales for restarting driving and motorcycle tests to show that the service for critical workers to apply for an emergency test closed on 14 August 2020.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="app-c-published-dates__change-item">
              <time class="app-c-published-dates__change-date timestamp" datetime="2020-08-03T16:26:07.000+01:00">3 August 2020</time>
              <p class="app-c-published-dates__change-note">Added the date that driving tests candidates who live in Wales will start to be invited by email to arrange their tests if it was cancelled because of coronavirus.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="app-c-published-dates__change-item">
              <time class="app-c-published-dates__change-date timestamp" datetime="2020-08-03T14:59:01.000+01:00">3 August 2020</time>
              <p class="app-c-published-dates__change-note">Added the indicative date that driving lessons will restart in Scotland.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="app-c-published-dates__change-item">
              <time class="app-c-published-dates__change-date timestamp" datetime="2020-07-21T22:17:41.000+01:00">21 July 2020</time>
              <p class="app-c-published-dates__change-note">Updated section 3 about car driving tests to confirm that the link that is emailed to pupils to arrange their test does not expire. Added information about what DVSA will do if the email address given for the booking does not work.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="app-c-published-dates__change-item">
              <time class="app-c-published-dates__change-date timestamp" datetime="2020-07-15T17:20:28.000+01:00">15 July 2020</time>
              <p class="app-c-published-dates__change-note">Added the date that approved driving instructor (ADI) part 3 (instructional ability) tests and ADI standards checks restart in England and Wales.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="app-c-published-dates__change-item">
              <time class="app-c-published-dates__change-date timestamp" datetime="2020-07-15T11:41:23.000+01:00">15 July 2020</time>
              <p class="app-c-published-dates__change-note">Added the dates that services will restart in Wales, and added information about car driving test candidates being emailed to choose a new test date.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="app-c-published-dates__change-item">
              <time class="app-c-published-dates__change-date timestamp" datetime="2020-07-10T18:39:00.000+01:00">10 July 2020</time>
              <p class="app-c-published-dates__change-note">First published.</p>
            </li>
        </ol>
      </div>
